	 Mumbai, Sept. 19: Videocon Industries and Bharat Petroresources Ltd, a wholly owned subsidiary of Bharat Petroleum Corporation Ltd, has acquired Brazils EnCana Brasil Petroleo Limitada for $283 million. Videocon and Bharat Petroresources will pay $165 million for the acquisition and another $118 million as reimbursement for EnCanas expenses since January 1, 2007.                            
